breakingChangesNotes: The scripts: GetRange, GetValuesOfMultipleFields, If-Then-Else, IgnoreFieldsFromJson, LastArrayElement, MapValuesTransformer, ModifyDateTime, PadZeros, ParseJSON, ProductJoin moved to **FiltersAndTransformers** pack. Make sure to update the **FiltersAndTransformers** pack to the latest version in order to use these scripts.
